{"id":8171,"date":"2020-04-11T09:30:58","date_gmt":"2020-04-11T09:30:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=8171"},"modified":"2022-08-30T01:31:04","modified_gmt":"2022-08-30T01:31:04","slug":"xu-hong-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/xu-hong-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\/","title":{"rendered":"XU H\u01af\u1edaNG THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T PH\u00d2NG NG\u1ee6 \u1ea4N T\u01af\u1ee2NG 2020"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 master \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian vun v\u00e9n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y cho ta nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y ri\u00eang t\u01b0 \u00fd ngh\u0129a. M\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, nh\u1eb1m mang t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7. V\u1eady trong n\u0103m 2020 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 n\u00e0o s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd? C\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/Byzannoithathiendai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Byzan<\/a> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/59801051_2529291067104668_5812339504639377408_o.jpg\" alt=\"xu-hung-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" class=\"wp-image-8180\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/59801051_2529291067104668_5812339504639377408_o.jpg 960w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/59801051_2529291067104668_5812339504639377408_o-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/59801051_2529291067104668_5812339504639377408_o-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>N\u00e9t t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n t\u00ednh t\u1ebf&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai mang m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ri\u00eang, th\u00ec s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u gia ch\u1ee7 \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thay v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0, r\u1ed1i m\u1eaft v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, n\u0103m 2020, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t thi\u00ean h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i h\u1ecdc m\u1ea1ch, s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/60032927_2529324673767974_5499362102453731328_o.jpg\" alt=\"xu-hung-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" class=\"wp-image-8177\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/60032927_2529324673767974_5499362102453731328_o.jpg 960w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/60032927_2529324673767974_5499362102453731328_o-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/60032927_2529324673767974_5499362102453731328_o-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/12-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"xu-hung-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" class=\"wp-image-8174\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/12-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/12-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/12-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/12-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/12-scaled.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n lu\u00f4n g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tr\u01a1n nh\u1eb5n, ph\u1ea3ng ph\u1ea5t tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p m\u1edbi l\u1ea1. \u0110\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111a d\u1ea1ng d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 g\u1ed7, kim lo\u1ea1i, k\u00ednh,&#8230;\u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n nghi cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n l\u00ean n\u00e9t \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t cho m\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng gian.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/logo-pn-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-8184\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/logo-pn-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/logo-pn-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/logo-pn-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/logo-pn.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"819\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/n1-1024x819.jpg\" alt=\"xu-hung-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" class=\"wp-image-8176\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/n1-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/n1-300x240.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/n1-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/n1-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/n1-scaled.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Byzan lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi gia ch\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u1eadt tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Nh\u1ea5n nh\u00e1 ch\u00fat c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed7i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1edf th\u00edch kh\u00e1c nhau, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n cho ph\u00f2ng master v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng \u00edt gia ch\u1ee7 trong n\u0103m 2020. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf m\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, Byzan lu\u00f4n kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, nh\u1ea5n nh\u00e1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 tinh th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"659\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/3b-1024x659.jpg\" alt=\"xu-hung-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" class=\"wp-image-8172\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/3b-1024x659.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/3b-300x193.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/3b-768x494.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/3b-1536x988.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/3b-scaled.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"658\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/4a-1024x658.jpg\" alt=\"xu-hung-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" class=\"wp-image-8173\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/4a-1024x658.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/4a-300x193.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/4a-768x494.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/4a.jpg 1450w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 theo phong c\u00e1ch Scandinavian<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Scandinavian lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0. L\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo l\u1ed1i ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac B\u1eafc \u00c2u, Scandinavian mang t\u1edbi cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng. \u0110i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng n\u1eefa cho phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, gi\u00fap ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u00ednh ti\u1ec7n nghi.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/scandinavian.jpg\" alt=\"xu-hung-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\" class=\"wp-image-8179\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/scandinavian.jpg 960w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/scandinavian-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/scandinavian-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, hi\u1ec7n nay t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean xanh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u xanh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng khi trong l\u00e0nh. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y, <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\">Byzan<\/a> \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong n\u0103m 2020. Hy v\u1ecdng qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-very-dark-gray-color has-very-light-gray-background-color has-text-color has-background\" href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/10-mau-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-sang-trong\/\" style=\"border-radius:50px\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem th\u00eam 10+ m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2020<\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 master \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian vun v\u00e9n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y cho ta nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y ri\u00eang t\u01b0 \u00fd ngh\u0129a. M\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, nh\u1eb1m mang t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":8180,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[155],"tags":[124,123,122],"class_list":["post-8171","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong-noi-that","tag-noi-that-phong-ngu-hien-dai","tag-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu","tag-xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8171","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href"